Business Brief -- Time Warner Inc.:
   Time Inc. Agrees to Acquire
   Arkansas Magazine Publisher
Time will acquire Leisure Arts from its two major
shareholders, Steve Patterson, president and chief executive
officer of Leisure Arts, and Stephens Inc., a Little Rock
investment firm.
   Time said Leisure Arts will complement the Oxmoor House
Inc. division of its Southern Progress Corp. unit. Both Time
and its parent are based in New York.